HEADWORD: Sandfish
<hw>Sand"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A small marine fish of the Pacific coast of North America
(<spn>Trichodon trichodon</spn>) which buries itself in the
sand.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

